{"tid":842774,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"「足球小將」當年小學全國決賽，個球證究竟收左明和幾多錢？","createTime":"2018-09-30T15:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T11:53:42.000Z","uid":2023,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b9a78845b55892b0f42f6da4acbb6594a0e83f","tid":842774,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:02:29.000Z","msg":"四、五條友圍住對面個皇牌，下下收山腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，瞄撚住隻腳黎剷，連波皮都hi唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小學雞踢波都咁撚狼死<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，個球證咁都唔比紅牌...知唔知佢差啲搞到2個未來世界級球星收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後戴志偉臨完場最後一個進攻，個球證夠膽死係人地射波前一秒吹完場雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，最後入左都當唔計<br />\n<br />\n你話個球證無收錢真係搵鬼信<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1317b6160bbf8e32031a93bb3fadf4bb9d4062b8","tid":842774,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786c60562b0e0470cc4e7e50871d83f9975af34b","tid":842774,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:14:15.000Z","msg":"一包蝦條"},{"pid":"e6102fb79f1367652cd1172e6331445099efe230","tid":842774,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:26:39.000Z","msg":"4424"},{"pid":"83fd17dc3ba65a0525491e60a3bd96d14a5bfaed","tid":842774,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:16:32.000Z","msg":"岬被人下下late tackle剷到腳都跛 對面都無食過牌"},{"pid":"5bdc93b2d6b84974e725b88633a245738823cf23","tid":842774,"uid":1453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"睇咁耐波未見過有球證係射波前吹雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69bf3e25d60ce6a384dd31a26905273e01a2091","tid":842774,"uid":3024